            <div class="field field--name-field-nir-lp-block-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h2 class="wsh_home mimic-h3">Transfer Agent and Registrar</h2><p>As a registered unitholder of IEP you can make use of the Internet services provided by our transfer agent, Computershare Investor Services. Whether changing an address, replacing a lost certificate, or transferring units, Computershare Investor Services will assist you through the necessary steps, give you forms and in many instances, permit you to complete the request on-line. Contact our transfer agent:</p><p><br><strong>Company name</strong>: ICAHN ENTERPRISES L.P.&nbsp;<br>Ticker Symbol: (NAS:IEP)&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Regular Mail:</strong><br>P.O. Box 43006<br>Providence, RI 02940-3006</p><p><strong>Overnight Delivery:&nbsp;</strong><br>150 Royall St., Suite 101<br>Canton, MA 02021</p><p><strong>Telephone</strong>:&nbsp;<br>Toll Free: 800 368 5948&nbsp;<br>Toll: +1 781 575 4223&nbsp;<br><br>Use Online Inquiry to manage your account and conduct transactions.&nbsp;</p></div>
      
</div>
      
  </div>
</div>
