            <div  class="panel-panel-inner">
              <div class="block-region-secondcolumn2"><div class="block-content--nir-lp-block block-content--nir-lp-block--16901 block--block-content8b6ce354-c286-46a1-88a7-283954754135 block--block-content8b6ce354-c286-46a1-88a7-283954754135--11511 block--secondcolumn2--block-content--8b6ce354-c286-46a1-88a7-283954754135 block--secondcolumn2--block-content--8b6ce354-c286-46a1-88a7-283954754135--11511 block--cb94f9c7-5673-46a4-bc1d-3c720863b779 block--cb94f9c7-5673-46a4-bc1d-3c720863b779--11511 block block-block-content block-block-content8b6ce354-c286-46a1-88a7-283954754135">
  
    
      
            <div class="field field--name-field-nir-lp-block-node field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item">  
            <div class="field field--name-field-nir-lp-block-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="field field--name-field-nir-global-block-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p><strong>Online Inquires</strong>:&nbsp;<a href="https://www-us.computershare.com/Investor/contact" target="_blank" aria-label="visit Computershare website">www-us.computershare.com/Investor/contact</a>&nbsp;<br>Computershare Investor Services General Contact Information:&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>By Mail</strong>:&nbsp;<br>Computershare Investor Services&nbsp;<br>P.O. Box 43006<br>Providence, RI 02940-3006</p><p><strong>By Overnight Delivery</strong>:&nbsp;<br>Computershare Investor Services&nbsp;<br>150 Royall St., Suite 101<br>Canton, MA 02021</p><h3 class="wsh_home">K-1</h3><p>The <a href="https://www.taxpackagesupport.com/icahn" target="_blank" aria-label="IEP Tax packages/K-1 are available on this link">IEP Tax packages/K-1 are available on this link:&nbsp;https://www.taxpackagesupport.com/icahn</a>.<br>The Tax packages/K-1 will be mailed out between March 16th and March 20th.</p></div></div>
      
